
Compiling
---------

  Just untar the sources and type make!


Testing
-------

  The hand daemon can be tested without installation by executing as:

  ./hand <command>

where <command> is the name of the command you want to start by hand.


Installing
----------

  The Makefile contains the $(BASE) variable, which controls the
install directory.  Set this as appropriate, and then type 'make install'.


Uninstalling
------------

  The package can be uninstalled with 'make uninstall'.
